#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:31 index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&krfb; is a server application that allows you to share your current session "
"with a user on another machine, who can use a <acronym>VNC</acronym> client "
"to view or even control the desktop."
msgstr ""
"&krfb; je strežniška aplikacija, ki vam omogoča skupno rabo trenutne seje z "
"uporabnikom na drugem računalniku, ki lahko uporablja odjemalca "
"<acronym>VNC</acronym>za ogled ali celo nadzor namizja."

